Changes from 1.6-0 to 1.7-0

*Bugs*

- Fixed bug #015723: eztagcloud is not multilangual
- Fixed bug #017601: eztagcloud will generate a fatal MySQL error if state based limitations are used

*Enhancements*

- Enable Google Chrome frame if installed on < IE 9
- Support for canonical link tag by sending canonical_url param with persistent_variable
- Simplified IE css matching using class on body tag if < IE 9
- Improved validation under XHTML strict and HTML 5
- Change use of old templateInit()/ezi18n() api and use class based api's introduced in 4.3 instead
